<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Spanish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [From the "24 Hours Newscast"] </F>
  [Text] Ten Colombian fishermen, including two boys, were 
detained minutes ago by members of the Venezuelan National Guard 
who entered Colombian territory. The fishermen were in a 
channel in La Rubiera Zone, east of Arauca. Other fishermen 
