<F P=100> Colombia </F>
<H3> <TI>   Top Cali Cartel Leader Reportedly Surrenders </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  PA1203155894 Hamburg DPA in Spanish 1528 GMT 12 Mar 94 </F>
<F P=103> PA1203155894 </F>
<F P=104>  Hamburg DPA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Spanish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Santa Fe de Bogota, 12 Mar (DPA) -- Julio Fabio 
Urdinola, a top leader of the Cali cocaine cartel, surrendered 
to Colombian authorities today, according to Radio Caracol, a 
private station in Bogota. 
  The report indicates that Urdinola surrendered to a 
prosecutor in the western city of Palmira. Also surrendering 
were Hector Porras and Ancizar Ardila, who were sought by 
Colombian authorities on drug trafficking charges. 

</TEXT>

