<H3> <TI>   Manuel Rodriguez Front Regional Leader Arrested </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  PY1503032094 Santiago Television Nacional de Chile Imagen 
Internacional in Spanish 0100 GMT 15 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> PY1503032094 </F>
<F P=104>  Santiago Television Nacional de Chile Imagen 
Internacional </F>



<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Spanish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] In Talca, Carabineros have arrested Misael Apablaza 
Basolado, 30, the third in command of the Manuel Rodriguez 
Front, FMR, Autonomous Faction. He was captured on Highway No. 5 
at Talca, where he was going to contact other criminals, but was 
intercepted by Carabineros who already were alerted to his 
arrival. 
  The terrorist was wounded in one leg when he tried to 
escape. 
He was admitted to the Talca regional hospital, where he is 
recovering. 
  Apablaza is regarded by police as the FMR Autonomous Faction 
leader responsible for recruiting minors for the FMR Autonomous 
Faction. 

