<H3> <TI>   World Bank Official Affirms Loan Disbursement </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  PA1503140194 </F>
<F P=103> PA1503140194 </F>
<F P=104></F>



<TEXT>
Article   Type:BFN 

  [Editorial Report] Guatemala City SIGLO VEINTIUNO in 
Spanish on 10 March, page 6, reports that, on 9 March, Claudio 
Sapelli, World Bank official on a two-week visit to Guatemala, 
affirmed that the International Bank for Reconstruction and 
Development will make its third loan disbursement during the 
second half of 1994. Guatemala has already received $48 million 
of the $120-million loan for the Economic Modernization program. 

